khapatnam\n| [[Pappala Chalapathirao]]\n|bgcolor=\"{{Telugu Desam Party/meta/color}}\"|\n| [[Telugu Desam Party]]\n| 18-06-2021\n|-\n| 17\n| Visakhapatnam\n| B. Naga Jagadeeswara Rao\n|bgcolor=\"{{Telugu Desam Party/meta/color}}\"|\n| [[Telugu Desam Party]]\n| 18-06-2021\n|-\n| 18\n| Guntur\n|'''Vacant'''\n|\n|'''TBD'''\n| 18-06-2021\n|-\n| 19\n| Prakasam\n|'''Vacant'''\n|\n|'''TBD'''\n| 18-06-2021\n|-\n| 20\n| Anantapur\n|'''Vacant'''\n|\n|'''TBD'''\n| 18-06-2021\n\n|}\n\n===Elected By Members Of Legislative Assembly===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! #\n! Constituency\n! Member\n! colspan=\"2\"| Party\n! Term\n|-\n| 1\n| Guntur\n| Janga Krishna Murthy\n|bgcolor=\"{{YSR Congress Party/meta/color}}\"|\n| [[YSR Congress Party]]\n| 29-03-2025\n|-\n| 2\n| East Godavari\n| [[Yanamala Ramakrishnudu]]\n|bgcolor=\"{{Telugu Desam Party/meta/color}}\"|\n| [[Telugu Desam Party]]\n| 29-03-2025\n|-\n| 3\n| Krishna\n| Parchuri Ashok Babu\n|bgcolor=\"{{Telugu Desam Party/meta/color}}\"|\n| [[Telugu Desam Party]]\n| 29-03-2025\n|-\n| 4\n| Visakhapatnam\n| Duvvarapu Rama Rao\n|bgcolor=\"{{Telugu Desam Party/meta/color}}\"|\n| [[Telugu Desam Party]]\n| 29-03-2025\n|-\n| 5\n| Kurnool\n| B Tirumala Naidu\n|bgcolor=\"{{Telugu Desam Party/meta/color}}\"|\n| [[Telugu Desam Party]]\n| 29-03-2025\n|-\n| 6\n| Kurnool\n| Challa Ramakrishna Reddy\n|bgcolor=\"{{YSR Congress Party/meta/color}}\"|\n| [[YSR Congress Party]]\n| 29-03-2023\n|-\n| 7\n| Guntur\n| Mopidevi Venkata Ramana Rao\n|bgcolor=\"{{YSR Congress Party/meta/color}}\"|\n| [[YSR Congress Party]]\n| 29-03-2023\n|-\n| 8\n| Kurnool\n| Gangula Prabhakar Reddy\n|bgcolor=\"{{YSR Congress Party/meta/color}}\"|\n| [[YSR Congress Party]]\n| 29-03-2023\n|-\n| 9\n| Krishna\n| Batchula Arjunudu \n|bgcolor=\"{{Telugu Desam Party/meta/color}}\"|\n| [[Telugu Desam Party]]\n| 29-03-2023\n|-\n| 10\n| Guntur\n| [[Nara Lokesh]]\n|bgcolor=\"{{Telugu Desam Party/meta/color}}\"|\n| [[Telugu Desam Party]]\n|29-03-2023