5727 }}\n* Chatterjee, R. 2007  [https://www.sciencemag.org/news/2007/01/portrait-killer \"Portrait of a Killer\"]. ''Science Magazine'' 117(2).\n* {{cite journal |author1=Chaulk C. Patrick |author2=Kazandjian Vah\u00e9 | year = 2004 | title = Moving Beyond Randomized Controlled Trials | url = | journal = American Journal of Public Health | volume = 94 | issue = 9| page = 1476 | doi=10.2105/ajph.94.9.1476|pmid=15333296 | pmc=1448474}}\n* {{cite journal |author1=Cohen Craig |author2=Duerr Ann |author3=Pruithithada Niwat |author4=Rugpao Sungwal |author5=Garcia Patricia |author6=Nelson Kenrad |author7=Hillier Sharon | year = 1995 | title = Bacterial Vaginosis and HIV Seroprevalence among Female Commercial Sex Workers in Chiang Mai, Thailand | url = | journal = AIDS | volume = 9 | issue = 9| pages = 1093\u201398 | doi=10.1097/00002030-199509000-00017|pmid=8527084 }}\n* Chu, P., Santos, G.-M., Vu, A., Nieves-Rivera, G., Colfax, J., Grinsdale, S., Huang, S., Phillip, S., Scheer, S. and Aragon, T. 2012 Impact of syndemics on people living with HIV in San Francisco. Presented at the XIX International AIDS Conference, Washington, D.C. (MOACO202 Oral Abstract).\n* {{cite journal |author1=Conant K. |author2=Kaleeba J. | year = 2013 | title = Dangerous liaisons: molecular basis for a syndemic relationship between Kaposi's sarcoma and P. falciparum malaria | url = | journal = Frontiers in Microbiology | volume = 4 | issue = | page = 35 | doi = 10.3389/fmicb.2013.00035 |pmid=23487416 |pmc=3594938 }}\n* {{cite journal |author1=Correa-Oliveira R. |author2=Golgher D. |author3=Oliveira G. |author4=Carvalho O. |author5=Massara C. |author6=Caldas I. |author7=Colley D. |author8=Gazzinelli G. | year = 2002 | title = Infection with Schistosoma mansoni correlates with altered immune responses to Ascaris lumbricoides and hookworm | url = | journal = Acta Tropica | volume = 83 | issue = 2| pages = 123\u201332 | doi=10.1016/s0001-706x(02)00108-0|pmid=12088853 }}\n* {{cite journal |author1=Cui Yang |author2=Koblin Beryl | year = 2011 | title = Migration, Neighborhoods, and Networks: Approaches to Understanding How Urban Environmental Conditions Affect Syndemic Adverse Health Outcomes Among Gay, Bisexual and Other Men Who Have Sex With Men | url = | journal = AIDS and Behavior | volume = 15 | issue = Suppl 1| pages = S35\u2013S50 | doi=10.1007/s10461-011-9902-5|pmid=21369730 | pmc=3084486}}\n* {{cite journal | author = Daftary A | year = 2012 | title = HIV and tuberculosis: The construction and management of double stigma | url = | journal = Social Science & Medicine | volume = 74 | issue = 10| pages = 1512\u201319 | doi=10.1016/j.socscimed.2012.01.027| pmid = 22444460 }}\n* {{cite journal |author1=Daftary A. |author2=Padayatchi N. | year = 2012 | title = Social constraints to TB/HIV healthcare: Accounts from coinfected patients in South Africa | url = | journal = AIDS Care | volume =  24| issue = 12| pages = 1480\u201386| doi=10.1080/09540121.2012.672719|pmid=22530855 |pmc=3484188 }}\n* {{cite journal | author = Santis De, Joseph Layerla, Dennys Barroso, Susana Gattamorta, Karina Sanchez, Michael, Prado Guillermo | year = 2012 | title = Predictors of Eating Attitudes and Behaviors Among Gay Hispanic Men | url = | journal = Archives of Nursing | volume = 26 | issue = 2| pages = 111\u2013126 | doi=10.1016/j.apnu.2011.06.003| pmid = 22449559 }}\n* {{cite journal |author1=Dyer T. |author2=Shoptaw S. |author3=Guadamuz T. |author4=Plankey M. |author5=Kao U. |author6=Ostrow D. |author7=Chmiel J. |author8=Herrick A. |author9=Stall R. | year = 2012 | title = Application of Syndemic Theory to Black Men Who Have Sex with Men in the Multicenter AIDS Cohort Study | url = | journal = Journal of Urban Health | volume = 89 | issue = 4| pages = 697\u2013708 | doi=10.1007/s11524-012-9674-x | pmid=22383094|pmc=3535137 }}\n* Easton, Delia 2004  The Urban Poor: Health Issues.  ''Encyclopedia of Medical Anthropology'', Volume 1, pp.&nbsp;207\u201313.  New York: Kluwer Academi